==Pentads==

*鴻雁來, 'The wild geese come' - referring to the southward migration of geese. 
*玄鳥歸, 'The dark birds return' - 'dark birds' refer to swallows. 
*群鳥養羞, 'Birds stock their hoards' - i.e. in preparation for winter.

