ba earthquake|1937-07-26]] ||[[Puebla]], [[Veracruz]]|| 7.3 M<sub>s</sub> || IX || 34 || || || |- | [[1932 Jalisco earthquakes|1932-06-22]] ||[[Colima]]|| 7.0 || VIII || || || Tsunami || |- | [[1932 Jalisco earthquakes|1932-06-18]] ||[[Colima]]|| 7.8 || VIII || || || Tsunami || |- | [[1932 Jalisco earthquakes|1932-06-03]] ||[[Jalisco]]|| 8.1 || X || 400 || || Tsunami || |- | [[1931 Oaxaca earthquake|1931-01-15]] ||[[Oaxaca]]|| 7.8 || X || 114 || || || |- | 1920-01-03 ||[[Puebla]], [[Veracruz]]|| 7.8 M<sub>s</sub> || X–XII || 648–4,000 || 167 || || {{harvnb|NGDC}} |- | 1912-11-19 ||[[State of Mexico]]|| 7.0<ref>http://www.geociencias.unam.mx/~ger/2003_Tectonophisics_Qro.pdf</ref> || VIII || || || || |- | [[1911 Guerrero earthquake|1911-12-16]] ||[[Guerrero]]|| 7.6 || IX || || || || |- | [[1911 Michoacán earthquake|1911-06-07]] ||[[Michoacán]]|| 7.6 || IX || 45 || || || |- | 1909-07-30 ||[[Guerrero]]|| 7.6 || IX || || || || |- | [[1907 Guerrero earthquake|1907-04-15]] ||[[Guerrero]]|| 7.7 || VIII || || || || |- | 1900-01-20 ||[[Colima]]|| 7.4 || VII || || || || |- | 1899-01-24 ||[[Guerrero]]|| 7.5 || VII || || || || |- | 1897-06-05 ||[[Oaxaca]]|| 7.4 || VII || || || || |- | 1894-11-02 ||[[Guerrero]], [[Oaxaca]]|| 7.4 || VIII || || || || |- | [[1892 Laguna Salada earthquake|1892-02-24]] ||[[Baja California]]|| 7.1–7.2 || X || 0 || || || |- | 1890-12-02 ||[[Guerrero]], [[Oaxaca]]|| 7.3 || VII || || || || |- | 1889-09-06 ||[[Guerrero]]|| 7.1 || VI || || || || |- | 1887-05-29 ||[[Guerrero]]|| 7.3 || VIII || || || || |- | [[1887 Sonora earthquake|1887-05-03]] ||[[Sonora]]|| 7.6 M<sub>w</sub> || || 51 || || || |- | 1882-07-19 ||[[Guerrero]], [[Oaxaca]]|| 7.5 || IX || || || || |- | 1879-05-17 ||[[Puebla]]|| 7.1 || VIII || || || || |- | 1875-03-09 ||[[Colima]], [[Jalisco]]|| 7.4 || VII || || || || |- | 1875-02-11 ||[[Jalisco]]|| 7.5 || VIII || || || || |- | 1874-03-16 ||[[Guerrero]]|| 7.3 || VII || || || || |- | 1872-03-27 ||[[Oaxaca]]|| 7.4 || VI || || || || |- | 1870-05-11 